{"tid":1276352,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家盡快傾下一步行動","createTime":"2019-07-02T02:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T05:35:15.000Z","uid":67232,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"87f32572434e01890e8373b43d17635c8277be5f","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:42:47.000Z","msg":"經過琴晚單野之後，我相信大家而家都士氣高漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但我哋嘅訴求係仲未達成架</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以請大家繼續做實事先，文宣而家有手足做咗好多野，請大家一齊forward出去啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而出街示威呀，十八區遍地開花，呢d仲未有討論。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無可否認，琴日衝立法會的確可能會令小部分人反感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以到和理非嘅回合啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我建議<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢幾日集中擺街站</span></span>，繼續宣傳同聚焦翻我哋嘅訴求，同時<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">每區組織小組去同擺電視機喺到嘅老人家去進行交流嘅行動</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，唔好比人帶走個風向。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民意都有一定程度上嘅重要性，都要爭取返嘅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之前都有人出post講個話要動員嘅行動太密，會令人好攰同埋無用，所以有幾次圍律政同特首辦。<br />\n<br />\n我同意嘅，所以請下一步大型行動係有計劃地plan好要達到咩目的，過程可以在場度。(最好度埋，但連登多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"55caff0a09ec861f3a26b2a150b9f57feea758e6","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:43:23.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d04a2c07fa1d75d80ae04adeca4f6f797cd5b8","tid":1276352,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:44:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"75a7ae600a783a7c9ae4c5bded0affc130416b0b","tid":1276352,"uid":170091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:45:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe62ea3b7c929b5627f6753306e493c83e004a27","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:56:52.000Z","msg":"大家要傾下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4431136fcd10c1df00f5311a248806d27aca020","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"街站gogogo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09037c007d42660423f1d561531c26e5ae1f459c","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"地區宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93594a86eb90fb0a10103514335581b7289a2cd","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"反擊對家宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5f71e972f5cdf7e3ff95097a3818a599f1f3ab","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:58:50.000Z","msg":"唔好沉醉於我哋自己嘅世界先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，雖然而家我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a73e43051e8900a73d855cbf4233f3678e027a35","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:22:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92a81030837a437dcaa04ecec72622cd17cc10bc","tid":1276352,"uid":134747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:35:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff25a33ce18fcde8c7235d9ffd5cbb9579755cac","tid":1276352,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:43:56.000Z","msg":"和理非做下文宣先<br />\n其他人要抖抖回氣，尤其係心理壓力"},{"pid":"b3751ef2bd66dea9ead5376c60392cb83a2814d5","tid":1276352,"uid":120856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d81f8aa1d6d59e69c43884371ab450e7b7a1ce21","tid":1276352,"uid":80763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"7月6有光復屯門行動<br />\n可以發大黎搞"},{"pid":"7d0868a608f9f6532bfa1e043f8951ded49e994f","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d81f8aa1d6d59e69c43884371ab450e7b7a1ce21","tid":1276352,"uid":80763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T03:52:10.000Z","msg":"7月6有光復屯門行動<br />\n可以發大黎搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"似係兩回事，一個係班大媽同阿伯喺到賣淫，一個係反送中同政制改革，我驚會混攪埋一齊講，失焦。<br />\n<br />\n但你問我我光復屯門我會join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，但就唔會以反送中之名搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6966a994509af716b8b2452c47865070a5c9707f","tid":1276352,"uid":67232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T04:19:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bc0f90c02f3a